dy-180988673/</link><description>针对感染和疾病的 T 细胞在餐后会变得更加有效。这一发现可能有助于改善抗癌疗法并优化我们对疫苗的反应</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 15:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/youve-been-told-to-feed-a-cold-turns-out-eating-may-truly-boost-your-immune-system-cells-according-to-a-new-study-180988673/</guid></item><item><title>冥王星能再次被视为行星吗？美国宇航局局长的新言论凸显了科学家之间的持久争论</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/could-pluto-once-again-be-considered-a-planet-new-remarks-from-nasas-administrator-highlight-an-enduring-debate-among-scientists-180988671/</link><description>二十年前，定义和命名天体的国际天文学联合会重新定义了行星的标准，将冥王星纳入矮行星的新类别</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 15:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/could-pluto-once-again-be-considered-a-planet-new-remarks-from-nasas-administrator-highlight-an-enduring-debate-among-scientists-180988671/</guid></item><item><title>在 2026 年 Met Gala 之前，大都会艺术博物馆推出了受真人启发的多种体型的新人体模型</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ahead-of-the-2026-met-gala-the-metropolitan-museum-of-art-introduced-new-mannequins-with-diverse-body-types-inspired-by-real-people-180988670/</link><description>新的“服装艺术”展览将艺术品与服装搭配，其中一些展示在通过 3D 打印制作的定制人体模型上</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 22:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ahead-of-the-2026-met-gala-the-metropolitan-museum-of-art-introduced-new-mannequins-with-diverse-body-types-inspired-by-real-people-180988670/</guid></item><item><title>宝瓶座埃塔流星雨本周达到顶峰，但明亮的月亮可能会破坏这场表演</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-eta-aquarid-meteor-shower-peaks-this-week-but-a-bright-moon-might-spoil-the-show-180988669/</link><description>这项一年一度的活动在 5 月 5 日晚上到第二天早上达到高峰，来自哈雷彗星留下的碎片痕迹。最好从南半球观看，但北半球的天文爱好者也可以一睹它的风采</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 20:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-eta-aquarid-meteor-shower-pea