smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-do-cows-burp-up-so-much-planet-warming-methane-a-newly-discovered-structure-in-their-gut-microbes-could-be-a-culprit-180988664/</link><description>一项新的研究表明，“氢体”是某些微生物体内的细胞器，这些微生物生活在牛、绵羊和山羊的特殊胃室中</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 16:02:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/why-do-cows-burp-up-so-much-planet-warming-methane-a-newly-discovered-structure-in-their-gut-microbes-could-be-a-culprit-180988664/</guid></item><item><title>新发现表明，苏格兰的这个岛屿实际上是一个人造的迷你陆地，坐落在一个木制平台上</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-island-in-scotland-is-actually-a-man-made-mini-landmass-resting-on-a-wooden-platform-new-discovery-shows-180988674/</link><description>科学家在调查克兰诺格遗址时在水下考古技术和摄影测量方面取得了重大进展</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 15:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-island-in-scotland-is-actually-a-man-made-mini-landmass-resting-on-a-wooden-platform-new-discovery-shows-180988674/</guid></item><item><title>在一项新研究中，人工智能在诊断现实世界的急诊患者方面优于医生。这并不意味着计算机将取代临床医生</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ai-outperformed-doctors-at-diagnosing-real-world-er-patients-in-a-new-study-that-doesnt-mean-computers-will-replace-clinicians-180988660/</link><description>OpenAI 的大型语言模型之一在多项实验中表现优于医生，暗示人工智能辅助紧急医疗护理可能指日可待</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ai-outperformed-doctors-at-diagnosing-real-world-er-patients-in-a-new-study-that-doesnt-mean-computers-will-replace-clinicians-180988660/</guid></item><item><title>参观挪威迄今为止发现的最大的维京时代宝藏。藏有近 3,000 枚硬币并且还在不断增加，这是一次千载难逢的发现</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-largest-viking-age-hoard-ever-found-in-norway-at-nearly-3000-coins-and-counting-the-cache-is-a-once-in-a-lifetime-find-180988657/</link><description>埋藏于 11 世纪中叶的藏品包括克努特大帝 (Cnut the Great)、未准备者埃塞尔雷德 (Aethelred the Unready)